casebody.data:
Miss Susan, Inc., et al., Respondents, v. Enterprise & Century Undergarment Co., Inc., Appellant.

Order unanimously reversed, with $20 costs and disbursements and items of disbursements, to wit, $613.25 for stenographer’s fees and $55.50 for process server’s fees disallowed. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Townley, Glennon, Cohn and Callahan, JJ.
